sources.description:
When 14 year-old Angel, an undocumented Latino, loses his older brother to the US Military in an attempt to earn naturalization for the family, he looks to a local street gang for brotherhood. PG-13

Directed by Miriam Kruishoop
2013
Starring Manny Perez, Vivica A. Fox, Richard Cabra, Noel Gugliemi, Paige Hurd, Angel Amaral, McKinley Freeman
